  "title": "Applied Cooking",
  "description": "A mod that allows Applied Energistics 2 and Cooking for Blockheads to work together!",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Refined Cooking Url\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/refined-cooking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Check%20out%20my%20other%20mod%20that%20connects%20Refined%20Storage%20and%20Cooking%20for%20Blockheads-Link%20at%20the%20bottom-e78a4e?labelColor=7f1620&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Refined Cooking Promo\" width=\"800\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Applied_Cooking/BH_AC_Header.png\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Header\" width=\"1125\" height=\"378\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Available%20for%20Forge-1.19%20%7C%201.18-edbd7e?labelColor=154a48&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Minecraft Versions Badge\" width=\"266\" height=\"28\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Install%20on-Client%20&amp;%20Server-edbd7e?labelColor=154a48&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Install Badge\" width=\"240\" height=\"28\" /></p>\n<p><a title=\"Melon Cube Partner Promo\" href=\"https://meloncube.net/sebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Applied_Cooking/BH_AC_Promo.png\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Promo\" width=\"1808\" height=\"268\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Applied_Cooking/BH_AC_Description.png\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Description\" width=\"1808\" height=\"179\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A mod that allows Applied Energistics 2 and Cooking for Blockheads to work together!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">One new block was added. The Kitchen Station!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Before you place the Kitchen Station as part of the CFB kitchen network, you need to configure it as if it were a Wireless Terminal. For Minecraft versions below 1.20, you need to do so in an AE2 Security Terminal. And for Minecraft versions 1.20+, you need to do so in an AE2 Wireless Access Point.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Once everything is connected, you'll be able to consume items from your AE2 network inventory right from your cooking table.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Applied_Cooking/BH_AC_Recipes.png\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Recipes\" width=\"1808\" height=\"824\" /></p>\n<h2>Blocks</h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>&nbsp;</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Connected</strong></span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Disconnected</strong></span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Kitchen Station&nbsp;</strong></span></td>\n<td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/19RvTpK/appliedcooking-kitchenstation-connected.png\" alt=\"Kitchen Station Connected\" width=\"397\" height=\"376\" /></td>\n<td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/brxMbvZ/appliedcooking-kitchenstation-disconnected.png\" alt=\"Kitchen Station Disconnected\" width=\"430\" height=\"376\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Applied_Cooking/BH_AC_Screenshot.png\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Screenshot\" width=\"1808\" height=\"824\" /></p>\n<h2>Socials</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Sebastrn's Curseforge\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/itssebastrn/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=ItsSebastrn&amp;color=edbd7e&amp;labelColor=154a48&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Curseforge\" width=\"148\" height=\"28\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Modrinth\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Sebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Sebastrn&color=edbd7e&labelColor=154a48&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Modrinth\" width=\"125\" height=\"28\" style=\"max-height: 28px;\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ItsSebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=@ItsSebastrn&amp;color=edbd7e&amp;labelColor=154a48&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=twitter&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Twitter\" width=\"159\" height=\"28\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Youtube\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC46TYUp8WpcFub8NxuGA66A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Sebastrn&amp;color=edbd7e&amp;labelColor=154a48&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Youtube\" width=\"125\" height=\"28\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Twitch\" href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/itssebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=ItsSebastrn&amp;color=edbd7e&amp;labelColor=154a48&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=twitch&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Twitch\" width=\"148\" height=\"28\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Github\" href=\"https://github.com/Sebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Sebastrn&amp;color=edbd7e&amp;labelColor=154a48&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Github\" width=\"125\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Refined Cooking Url\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/refined-cooking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Applied_Cooking/BH_AC_RCLink.png